    "# 01 - Data Audit and Augmentation Pipeline\n",
    "Augmentation is designed specifically to break scene-level shortcuts: color jitter and grayscale conversion prevent the model from relying on belt lighting patterns; aggressive random erasing forces attention to multiple object regions."
   ]
  },
